    "uen": "201924585G",
    "description": "<p>Since our establishment in 2013, Cleaning Network Singapore (CNS) has been a steadfast provider of commercial cleaning, maintenance, and facilities management services.</p>\n<p>Our enduring commitment to excellence empowers us to meet the ever-evolving needs of our clients, offering unwavering dedication to delivering quality, efficiency, and reliability.</p>\n<p>At CNS, we recognisethat our most valuable assets are our people and technology. We invest substantially in the training and development of our staff, equipping them with the expertise needed to provide exceptional services. Moreover, we maintain our position at the forefront of the industry through the adoption of cutting-edge cleaning technologies and equipment.</p>\n<p>Central to our core values is the cultivation of robust client relationships, and we take immense pride in fulfilling our commitments. Remarkably, 90% of our business emanates from repeat customers and referrals—an irrefutable endorsement of our steadfast commitment and service excellence.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Specialise on:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Management Cleaning</p>\n<p>Stewarding</p>\n<p>Office Cleaning</p>\n<p>Industrial Cleaning</p>\n<p>Home Cleaning</p>\n<p>Spring Cleaning</p>\n<p>Event Cleaning</p>",
